<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>xīn nián gē 迦南225</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 dōng qù chūn lái rì chū rì luò cān fēng lù sù yī tóng dù guò
 xīn nián lái dào nǐ yī shēng hǎo zhù nǐ shēn tǐ jiàn kāng xīn zhōng méi fán nǎo
 zhēn chéng de shuō yī shēng nǐ men xīn kǔ le
 ài de tuán jù nán wàng jīn xiāo
 ài huǒ rán shāo qián chéng qí dǎo tuō qǐ lí míng de tài yáng
 gēn suí shèng líng yǐn dǎo.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>225</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>